		<title>Dog Training And/Or What Comes Next</title>
		<link>http://www.frivoli.com/caninenation/archives/dog-training-andor-what-comes-next</link>
		<comments>http://www.frivoli.com/caninenation/archives/dog-training-andor-what-comes-next#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 29 Apr 2012 05:30:39 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Eric Brad</dc:creator>
