			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Audio edition of the article <a href="http://lhttp://lifeasahuman.com/2012/pets/learn-positive-dog-training/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><strong>Learn Positive Dog Training</strong></a> from the Life As A Human online magazine website. You can visit <a href="http://caninenation.lifeasahuman.com/" target="_blank">Life as a Human</a> to find this and other articles.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.frivoli.com/caninenation/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/learn-positive1.jpg"><img class="alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-1011" title="learn positive" src="http://www.frivoli.com/caninenation/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/learn-positive1-290x290.jpg" alt="" width="290" height="290" /></a>Have you heard about positive training but aren’t sure what it is or how to get started?  Well, I can give you a road map to success with four great books to get you on your way!</p>
<p>These four books cover different aspects of a positive approach to training and living with our dogs.  Below are links to each of the books mentioned in this podcast from Dogwise.com</p>
