			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Audio edition of the article <a href="http://lifeasahuman.com/2011/pets/demystifying-the-behaviour-of-dogs/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><strong>Demystifying the Behaviour of Dogs</strong></a> from the Life As A Human online magazine website. You can visit <a href="http://lifeasahuman.com/category/pets/canine-nation/" target="_blank">Life a a Human</a> to find this and other articles.</p>
