<a href="http://www.kathysdao.com/articles/Forget_About_Being_Alpha_in_Your_Pack.html" target="_blank">Internationally respected animal trainer Kathy Sdao talks about dogs, packs, and alphas.</a></p>
<p>This week&#8217;s recommendation is <a href="http://drsophiayin.com/" target="_blank">&#8220;Veterinarian Dr. Sophia Yin&#8217;s website.</a> This site is a great resource that has insightful blog articles by Dr. Yin as well as many great resources for dog owners and professional dog trainers alike. Check it out and see what Dr. Yin has to say!</p>
